  "text": "10) IA [CITATION_1] : or improved A+ is the result of a generic 7-way strategy proposed by its authors for the amelioration of any given SR method. The last three methods are important as they are part of a counter-narrative against CNN strategies and one can find SRCNN in their comparisons.",
